title: L'emploi du temps (Time Out, Laurent Cantet, 2001) DVDRip
description:
The film tells the story of Vincent, a middle-aged man who is laid off after having spent more than 11 years working for a prestigious consulting firm. Unable to admit to his family that he has been fired, the unemployed executive continues to pretend he is going to the office every day. In reality, Vincent spends his time aimlessly driving the highways of France and Switzerland, reading papers, or sleeping in his car. - Wikipedia (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Time_Out_%282001_film%29)
